So that's one possibility for

00:00:01.670 --> 00:00:05.670
selecting a metric to quantify the popularity of brands of candy.

00:00:05.670 --> 00:00:08.300
The number of turns between selections of candy,

00:00:08.300 --> 00:00:10.750
otherwise known as the inter-selection time.

